title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Dhaka · ★4.67 · 1 bedroom · 1 bath
listing_description: A cozy room in Gulshan with AC, fast Wi-Fi, large kitchen, dining and living rooms with additional lounge. Flat is equipped with washing machine, cable TV, coffee machine, multiple terrace and lounge areas for you to relax, work and hangout. It’s right inside Gulshan which is the most upscale neighbourhood in Dhaka - safe for foreigners and families for both short and long term stay. There is a patisserie and café just next to the building.
